<P>
Photo, Cleveland's Jerry Browne prepares to tag out Yankees' Steve Sax, who is 
attempting to steal second base in the third inning, and umpire Greg Kosc 
prepares to make the call. Indians won, 4-3, to sweep the Yankees. Associated 
Press 
</P>
