driving and child endangerment, San Diego police said. 
</P>
<P>
Lindsey C. Jackson, 34, was reportedly driving east in the wrong lane of 
traffic on the highway, about 3 miles east of Bandy Canyon Road, when he 
swerved and hit an embankment and his truck rolled over, a police spokesman 
said. 
</P>
<P>
