NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Isiah Thomas of the Detroit Pistons will miss up to three weeks because of a 
broken finger suffered in a fight that prompted his two-game suspension. 
</P>
<P>
Thomas, ejected with the Chicago Bulls' Bill Cartwright in the first quarter of 
