on training flight to prepare for round-the-world peace expedition to begin 
June 5. KARI RENE HALL / Los Angeles Times; Map, Color, FRIENDSHIP FLIGHT 1989 
ITINERARY, THOMAS PENIX / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
